## Page Layout — All States

### Persistent Elements (Appear in All States Except No Sprint)

**Page Header**
- Page title: "Execution & Review" — consistent with current build
- Subtitle: dynamic based on state (see state-specific content below)
- Top-right: settings icon (gear) — opens a small dropdown with: "Rename Sprint," "Close Sprint Early," "View Sprint History"

**Sprint Identity Block**
Appears directly below the page header. Always visible when a sprint exists.

| Element | Content | Editable |
|---|---|---|
| Sprint name | System default or founder-custom name | Yes — inline edit via pencil icon |
| Sprint goal | Full sprint goal text — always shown as subtitle | No — edit in Planning |
| Sprint status badge | PRE-LAUNCH / ACTIVE / WIND-DOWN / CLOSED | No — system-calculated |
| Sprint dates | "Started [date] · Ends [date]" or "Kicks off [date]" if pre-launch | No |
| Days remaining pill | "[N] days remaining" — shown in active and wind-down states only | No |

