## State 1 — No Sprint

### When It Renders
The founder has never locked a sprint plan, or all previous sprints are closed and no new sprint has been started.

### Layout
No sprint identity block. No navigation cards. A centered orientation state.

**Content:**
- Section icon — a simple compass or arrow icon, consistent with platform style
- Heading: *"Your execution layer is ready."*
- Body: two sentences maximum. *"Once you lock your sprint plan, this section becomes your operational home for the quarter — progress tracking, weekly standups, strategic synthesis, and your sprint retrospective all live here."*
- Single CTA button: "Go to Planning" — links to the Planning section

**What NOT to show:**
- No placeholder cards with locked states
- No statistics or progress elements
- No navigation cards in disabled state

The empty state should feel intentional and calm — not like something is broken or missing.

