## Data Model Requirements

The following fields are needed to power the Execution Overview page across all states. Flagged for Pass 3 data wiring.

| Field | Table | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| Sprint name | sprints | Founder-editable, defaults to system name |
| Sprint goal | sprint_goals | Read-only on this page |
| Sprint status | sprints — calculated field | Derived from kickoff_date, end_date, retrospective_complete |
| Lock date | sprints | Set at sprint lock |
| Kickoff date | sprints | Founder-set, nullable until confirmed |
| End date | sprints | Calculated: kickoff_date + 84 days |
| Sprint number | sprints | Auto-incremented per account |
| Milestone completion count | milestones — aggregated | count(status = Complete) / count(*) |
| Blocker count | milestones — aggregated | count(status = Blocked) |
| Last status update | milestones — max(updated_at) | Most recent milestone status change |
| Initiatives complete | initiatives — aggregated | count(all milestones complete) |
| Momentum synthesis last generated | momentum_syntheses — max(created_at) | |
| Launch summary shared | sprint_summaries — shared boolean | |
| Wind-down progress | wind_down_decisions — completion status | Steps 1/2/3 complete |
| Retrospective complete | retrospective_records — approved boolean | |
| Capability scores (start + end) | capability_scores — snapshots | Used in closed state summary |

