## Empty & Edge States Summary

| Scenario | Behavior |
|---|---|
| No sprint ever created | Orientation state — single CTA to Planning |
| Sprint locked, kickoff not set | Pre-launch banner with inline date picker |
| Sprint active, no status updates in 8+ days | Amber indicator on health bar and Status Tracker card |
| Sprint active, launch summary not shared | Action needed badge on Sprint Launch card |
| Sprint active, no momentum synthesis ever generated | Prompt treatment on Momentum Synthesis card |
| Wind-down period, wind-down not started | Amber wind-down banner with Begin CTA |
| Sprint closed, retrospective not started | Retrospective CTA banner as primary action |
| Retrospective complete | Celebration block + next sprint CTA |
| Multiple closed sprints, new sprint not started | State 6 layout with sprint history visible |

