## Design Decisions to Carry Forward

1. **Sprint name edit** is available from this page via inline pencil icon — this is the primary place founders will rename their sprint, not a settings page
2. **Kickoff date** is set from this page in the Pre-Launch state — it is not set during sprint lock, giving the founder intentional separation between locking the plan and starting the clock
3. **Sprint goal** is always visible on this page but never editable here — it is locked at sprint lock and any changes would require unlocking the sprint plan
4. **The Retrospective card** is always visible in some form across all active states — never hidden — so the founder always knows it is coming
5. **Sprint history** begins appearing in State 6 — it does not have its own navigation item in V1, it lives at the bottom of the Overview page

